data.description: Discover the allure of Lake Lindley Village with this charming 3-bed, 2-bath home, boasting a 2-car garage and a screened back porch. Freshly painted inside and out, recent upgrades include a NEW ROOF (2022) and NEW appliances (2023), knock-down ceilings, updated electrical outlets, light fixtures, and a NEW water heater (2023). The beautifully landscaped backyard offers privacy and serenity. Enjoy the convenience of NO HOA and a prime location near shopping, schools, Stetson University, and downtown DeLand. Schedule your showing today!
